VERSION 1
WHEN FILE_NAME_IS AndroidManifest.xml
WHEN CURRENT_FILE_MATCHES /android:exported\s*=\s*"(true|TRUE)"/i
OBSERVE PROJECT_HAS_GLOB **/AndroidManifest.xml AS manifest_files
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Exported Android components should be reviewed at component scope for missing permission or access-control boundaries.
TRACE Mobile RDL pilot evaluated this finding against Android manifest context instead of relying on inline RDL only.
